tosdr.case: Third parties used by the service are bound by confidentiality obligations

title: Third parties used by the service are bound by confidentiality obligations
quoteText:
We do not permit any of these service providers to collect any of your personal information on our sites or in our services, applications, or tools for their own purposes.
These service providers are subject to confidentiality agreements with us and other legal restrictions on their use or collection of any personal information.
